code: /**  * @return the valid set of {@link Setting}s for a {@value #TYPE} realm  */ public static Set<Setting.AffixSetting<?>> getSettings() {     final Set<Setting.AffixSetting<?>> settings = Sets.newHashSet(HTTP_SERVICE_KEYTAB_PATH, CACHE_TTL_SETTING, CACHE_MAX_USERS_SETTING, SETTING_KRB_DEBUG_ENABLE, SETTING_REMOVE_REALM_NAME).     settings.addAll(DelegatedAuthorizationSettings.getSettings(TYPE)).     settings.addAll(RealmSettings.getStandardSettings(TYPE)).     return settings. }
